g.text: Ways to link css to our HTML page
1. element level - tag-name {}, applies this style to all the tags
content-size default or box-sizing:content-box - width + padding-left + padding-right + border-left
div p - selects all p inside div
div>p - selects all p directly inside div
div+p - selects first p after div
div~p - selects all p after div
